con:soapui-project.name: AdapterSpringInjectionTest
con:soapui-project.con:description:
When unsecured adapter endpoints are used, security headers should never be present and vice versa. These tests do the following:
- Set services to use unsecured/secured endpoints - Create mock adapter endpoints and send adapter requests to these mock endpoints - Verify that security headers are not present for unsecured endpoints and vice-versa(via assertions set in the mock test steps)
